    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In nomine domini nostri Iehsu Christi dei eterni, anno ab incarnationis
                        eius millesimo centesimo quadragesimo tertio, quinto kalendas februarii,
                        indictione sexta. Manifesti sumus nos iugales <persName><name ref="Bonellus"
                                >Bonellus</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Boncius"
                                >Boncci</name></persName> filius et <persName><name ref="Scocta"
                                >Scocta</name></persName> coniux eius et filia quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Bonus">Boni</name></persName> atque
                                <persName><name ref="Balduinus">Baldovinus</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Hughicio">Ughiccio</name></persName> germani
                        filii quondam <persName><name ref="Iohannes">Iohannis</name></persName> quia
                        per hanc cartulam, sub notitia <persName><name ref="Martinus"
                            >Martini</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Iohannacis"
                                >Ioannichi</name></persName> et <persName><name ref="Signorellus"
                                >Signorelli</name></persName> filii <persName><name ref="Petrus"
                                >Petri</name></persName> qui propinquiores mihi esse videntur, a
                        quibus secundum legem interrogata et cognita sum nullam pati violentia (…)
                        vendimus et tradimus tibi <persName><name ref="Rubeus">Rubeo</name> de
                                <placeName ref="#places/3207" key="#Hospitals"
                                >Altepascio</placeName></persName>, ad opus <orgName
                            key="#Hospitals" ref="#juridical_persons/3206"><rs key="#Hospitals"
                                >hospitalis</rs> de iam dicto loco</orgName>, duas integras petias
                        de terra que videntur esse posite in loco et finibus qui dicitur <placeName
                            ref="#places/3202"
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Mention #Viscount"
                            >Cartialla</placeName>. Una quarum est tenens unum caput in via
                        pubblica, aliud in terra nostra quam reservamus nobis, latus unum tenet in
                        terra de <persName><name ref="Poellare de Tolle">Poellare de loco qui
                                    <placeName>Tolle</placeName> nuncupatur,</name></persName> aliud
                        in terra <persName><name ref="Rodulfinus">Rodufini</name></persName>. Alia
                        petia posita ibidem in Cartialla, est tenes unum caput in terra de
                        suprascripto Poellare, aliud in terra de filiis <persName><name
                                ref="Ildebrandinus Guttus">Ildebrandini Gutti</name></persName>,
                        latus unum tenet in terra de filiis <persName><name ref="Ursus Stantius"
                                >Ursi Stantei</name></persName>, aliud in <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Mention">terra</rs>
                        <rs key="#Viscount">vicecomitorum</rs> de <placeName ref="#places/3200"
                            key="#Viscount">Ficecclo</placeName>, et sunt inter ambas duodecim
                        stariora ad sextarium de duodecim panibus. (…). Pro quibus a te meritum
                        recepimus vice Martini domini tui et hospitalis iam dicti sex libras bonorum
                        denariorum lucensis monete. <ref>Pena in duplum.</ref> (…) Hanc cartulam
                        scribere rogavimus <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Heinricus"
                                >Henrigum</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarium</rs> donni inperatoris. Actum in Valle Arni, in
                        villa que <placeName ref="#places/3219">Caprognana</placeName> dicitur, non
                        longe ab domo suprascriptorum iugalium. Signa manus suprascriptorum iugalium
                        Bonelli et Scocte atque Balduini et Ughiccionis, qui hanc cartulam
                        venditionis fieri rogaverunt. Signa manus <persName><name ref="Lucterius"
                                >Lucterii</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Rodelandus"
                                >Rolandini</name></persName> et <persName><name ref="Buttrigus"
                                >Buttrighi</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Ursus"
                                >Ursi</name></persName> atque <persName><name ref="Normannus"
                                >Normanni</name></persName> filii <persName><name ref="Signorellus"
                                >Signorelli</name></persName>. Signa manus <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Ildebrandinus">Ildebrandini</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Lambertus">Lanberti</name></persName> atque
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Malpilius"
                            >Malpilii</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Raginmundus"
                                >Ramondini</name></persName> et aliorum rogatorum <rs key="#Witness"
                            >testium</rs>. (S) Henrigus donni inperatoris notarius post rogationem
                        et tradictionem complevi et dedi. Et repromissionem fieri rogaverunt contra
                        suprascriptam cartulam venditionis ad defendendum qui per manum tenet ad
                        penam optimi argenti trecentorum solidorum ad suprascriptum datare meritum
                        et testes et dit.</ab>
